sentences: Jennifer Finch (also Jennifer Precious Finch), born August 5, 1966, is an American musician, designer, and photographer most notable for being the primary bass player of the punk rock band L7.
Active in L7 from 1986 to 1996, Finch also wrote music and performed with her bands OtherStarPeople and The Shocker in the interim before joining the reunited L7 in 2014.
